<html>

<head>
	<title>Reservation Confirmation</title>
	<style type="text/css">
	div.reservationCard {
		background-color: #eeeeaa;
		color: #000000;
		padding: 1em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}
	
	div.reservationCard h2 {
		font-family: Palatino, serif;
		font-style: italic;
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 0px;
		font-size: 200%;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	div.reservationContainer {
		width: 50%;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	div.reservationContainer input {
		width: 100%;
		height: 3em;
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		font-size: 1em;
		font-weight: bold;
		border: 3px outset black;
		cursor: pointer;
	}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<p>Good news, <%= @reservation.user.name %>!</p>

<p>	You were on the waiting list for "<%= @reservation.session.topic.name %>",
	and space has become available! You have automatically been enrolled in the
	class, and need take no additional action to attend.</p>
	
<p>	If you won't be able to make it to this session after all, you can cancel
	your reservation <%= link_to "here", :controller => "reservations", :only_path => false %>.</p>

<div class="reservationContainer">
	<div class="reservationCard">
		<h2>Your Reservation</h2>
		<dl>
			<dt>What:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @reservation.session.topic.name %></dd>
			<dt>When:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @reservation.session.time %></dd>
			<dt>Where:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @reservation.session.location %></dd>
			<dt>Who:</dt>
			<dd><%=h @reservation.user.name %></dd>
		</dl>
	</div>
</div>

<p>You can use the attached ICS file to add the session to your calendar software.</p>
</body>

</html>

